  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Healthy adults with skewed, humped or broad nose, who are able to attend all
             follow-ups

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Inability to keep the research plan

          -  Allergies to components of the nasal brace

          -  Diseases of the bone metabolism

          -  Medication affecting bone metabolism

          -  Drugs or alcohol abuse
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
